{"tid":519544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★奴隸之育成----月薪$12,000當正間舖係自己開","createTime":"2018-01-04T12:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T03:20:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":146,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca4c4b5bd9ec2677f819afd16228a373c24cd23","tid":519544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"以我媽咪為例，佢做零售業，都叫做係資深員工，有時放假佢電話都會不停響起！不外乎都係其他同事問佢啲嘢擺喺邊，價錢折扣嗰啲點做之類。<br />\n<br />\n「唉好煩啊係咁打嚟！」<br />\n<br />\n「你放緊假，可以唔聽。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔得㗎，佢哋唔識會做錯晒！」<br />\n<br />\n「咁關你咩事&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「唉你唔明&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明，你人工只係高過佢哋$500，得嗰$12,000蚊返6日，每日踩10個鐘，咁上心做咩。最慘就係佢哋仲會為咗呢啲人哋嘅事，食唔安坐唔落，同佢行行吓街，佢都會走咗去打電話，精神長期崩緊，作為佢個仔望到都覺得心痛無奈。<br />\n<br />\n「啊仔，你等我一陣，我驚阿Mary搞錯啲數，我都係打返去公司問問。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隔咗一陣，又驚自己有甩漏。</span><br />\n「死啦，琴日呢隻洗面奶開始做優惠價，我有冇轉價錢牌呢？唉都係打返去問下好啲。」<br />\n<br />\n當你以為終於無事發生，可以同媽咪享受天倫之樂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">少年你太天真，佢哋可以天馬行空咁創造問題出嚟。</span><br />\n「死啦，我琴日好似漏咗同個客講歡迎光臨，死啦，佢個樣好似神秘顧客&hellip;&hellip;又要俾人照肺啦今次！」<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得各行各業都鐘意請我媽咪呢啲年齡層嘅做低下層，因為請佢哋好多時都唔需要高人工，又上心負責！我係呢到代表香港嘅有錢人，向母親你奉上最高敬意！獅子山精神無得頂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8A-%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B-%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-12-000%E7%95%B6%E6%AD%A3%E9%96%93%E8%88%96%E4%BF%82%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%96%8B-090638838.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2585%258B-%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA-12-000%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%2588%2596%25E4%25BF%2582%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E9%2596%258B-090638838.html&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ057TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a4ea246c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8A-%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B-%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-12-000%E7%95%B6%E6%AD%A3%E9%96%93%E8%88%96%E4%BF%82%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%96%8B-090638838.html</a>"},{"pid":"049b852883dcdbd34a61f230120cb2b71417d596","tid":519544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796497db4c0acab223030c559e2d0dd3857f7a7c","tid":519544,"uid":19454,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/094853_1f396d470c3a953a120336f14c9e53de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F094853_1f396d470c3a953a120336f14c9e53de.jpg&h=e21e43d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f1abc8a6ed57c0d9dffa519109a0def55b709e","tid":519544,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29f0ac375dfb187acfa9e3bd1d012cfbc832cd0","tid":519544,"uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"冇人理樓豬，我出去搵巨乳、蓋清、石丸、飛鳥入嚟撐場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496415a50cbedbee14b8a8f9753c98a7c6132841","tid":519544,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"老貓自推，變咗熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d4db83d765b5c869eca3794d61ca90be1f7a1e","tid":519544,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"有時係係心虛，可能冇交帶好"},{"pid":"9795305cc7f400730d1a9c121800436964760fb1","tid":519544,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"家用比多啲就可以叫媽媽唔駛做野<im